{"tid":1938110,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"4.7 吋和 5.5 吋，iOS 14 代碼揭露 iPhone 狗有大小雙版本","createTime":"2020-03-22T10:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T14:59:15.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e063d39d4db38d30863975d92213ec15ea6691a5","tid":1938110,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:24:31.000Z","msg":"iPhone SE 的後繼機款，可說近年來謎團最多的 Apple 新品了，到底何時將正式發表、正式名稱是甚麼等情報各界都還沒有定論，到底是叫做 iPhone SE 2、iPhone 9 還是就叫做 iPhone 都有各自的說法，同時 Touch ID 是否回歸也沒有很確定的答案。<br />\n<br />\n不過根據日前洩露的 iOS 14 代碼，iPhone SE 後繼機款除了傳聞中的 4.7 吋之外，還有一個 5.5 吋的稍大螢幕版本，且都具備 Touch ID 機能。<br />\n<br />\n名稱到底會是 iPhone SE 2 / iPhone 9 都還無法確認的 iPhone 新機 (以下一律暫稱為 iPhone 9)，先前多方傳聞指出外形設計和 iPhone 8 相當相似，將配置 4.7 吋螢幕和 A13 處理器，同時還會配置 Touch ID (也有傳聞指稱會有搭 Face ID 的版本)。<br />\n<br />\n而根據日前洩露出來的 iOS 14 程式碼， iPhone 9 除了 4.7 吋版本之外，還有一個 5.5 吋螢幕版本 (將叫做 iPhone 9 Plus？)，兩款 iPhone 9 預期將會取代當前還在銷售中的 iPhone 8 和 iPhone 8 Plus。還有， iOS 14 程式碼還顯示 4.7 吋和 5.5 吋版本的 iPhone 9 都具備 Touch ID 指紋辨識機能。<br />\n<br />\n另外，外界預期 Apple 會於 3 月底的春季發表會正式推出 iPhone 9，但此發表會因為疫情而宣布取消，所以有可能會直接在 Apple 官網上架。"},{"pid":"bcbefc3bb6f7995d9c6a974a5e3eec336e1090bc","tid":1938110,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:25:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/215450/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4544%2F215450%2F1%2F&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdPUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=ebe3ec0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/215450/1/</a>"},{"pid":"f125501a646f3792a69f5f6d2272679aa5ab034f","tid":1938110,"uid":255744,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:27:07.000Z","msg":"如果屬實，真係為出而出"},{"pid":"7ca1253044d7f063c417d4d85bc3416aca4d265e","tid":1938110,"uid":294,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:28:02.000Z","msg":"代碼只為相容iphone 8, iphone 8 plus<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"6f00f5c6bddc48fdbcf6fe1cea2affa0254fbd17","tid":1938110,"uid":129385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:45:13.000Z","msg":"又撚9"},{"pid":"09b7a7cfe9f0199161fd345f4be642cb980e0d30","tid":1938110,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c82538bd701ce6f63ad8fd6570ef462d94df41c","tid":1938110,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ca1253044d7f063c417d4d85bc3416aca4d265e","tid":1938110,"uid":294,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:28:02.000Z","msg":"代碼只為相容iphone 8, iphone 8 plus<br />\n<br />\n完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:13:12.000Z","msg":"also iPhone 7"},{"pid":"445c95eff14107aa01d1f5bf44018943d080d200","tid":1938110,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T14:59:15.000Z","msg":"我等24pro max"}]}